descriptionHtml:
Just a Harley Quinn character I felt like making. She\'s a level 1 nord. I have pictures of her taken with nothing but [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2332]Final Younger Characters[/url] by Toshiki, and [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3866]Harley Quinn Jester Outfit[/url] by Chocolambot.
I also took pictures of her with:
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2356]XCE - Xenius Character Enhancement[/url] by Xenius (what I use with the Final younger Characters)
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563]Coverwomen[/url] and [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4869]Covereyes[/url] by mrLenski
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812]Better Females[/url] by Bella.
author: Araenna
